---
// No-op marker component. The rehype-section-wrapper plugin removes this
// from the tree before render and uses its position to close the current
// .prose-section. Subsequent content sits outside any section until the
// next h2 starts a new one.
//
// Usage in MDX:
//
//   import SectionBreak from '$lib/components/section-break.astro';
//
//   ## A section
//
//   Content inside the section card.
//
//   <SectionBreak />
//
//   Content here renders outside any section card.
//
//   ## Next section
//
//   Back inside a section card.
---
